https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fdp%2FB0BWFSFD7P" class="rapid-with-clickid">新的 S95C</a> 。后者支持更快的 144Hz 刷新率，并通过外部盒子运行其端口，这使得设计更薄。其他<a data-i13n="cpos:45;pos:1" href="https://www.rtings.com/tv/reviews/samsung/s95c-oled">评论家</a><a data-i13n="cpos:46;pos:1" href="https://reviewed.usatoday.com/televisions/features/samsung-s95b-vs-samsung-s95c-which-should-you-buy">说它</a>也可以变得更亮一点。但目前 S95 55 英寸和 65 英寸型号的售价分别为<a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:47;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI2NmVhNTY3YS1jOTg3LTRjMmUtYTJmZi0wMjkwNGVmZGU2ZWEiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYW1hem9uLmNvbS9kcC9CMEJXRlNGRDdQP3RhZz1nZGd0MGMtcC1vLTEzNi0yMCIsImNvbnRlbnRVdWlkIjoiYWFkZDA1OTYtMTYwYi00ZWUyLWIyMDQtODEzNmFhYjljZTYzIn0&amp;signature=AQAAAdwL8-cCoYISluuCpJO0vG6PonGZoxkCPy14Ny1jajz7&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fdp%2FB0BWFSFD7P" class="rapid-with-clickid">2,298 美元</a>和<a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:48;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI2NmVhNTY3YS1jOTg3LTRjMmUtYTJmZi0wMjkwNGVmZGU2ZWEiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYW1hem9uLmNvbS9kcC9CMEJXRlQyNjJQP3RhZz1nZGd0MGMtcC1vLTEzNi0yMCIsImNvbnRlbnRVdWlkIjoiYWFkZDA1OTYtMTYwYi00ZWUyLWIyMDQtODEzNmFhYjljZTYzIn0&amp;signature=AQAAAd4GA6uCD-GkPlZHeSKv5H2jrrrfJ6u9R5-XoF0-V4Hp&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fdp%2FB0BWFT262P" class="rapid-with-clickid">2,298 美元</a>，而且其升级似乎不足以证明对大多数人来说额外的成本是合理的。如果您正在市场上购买高端电视，那么 S95B 在有货的情况下应该会保持更好的价值。</p><h2> Roku 流媒体棒 4K </h2><p><core-commerce id="32b2602d5ee943ad8c991878975afdd5" data-type="product