减少烹饪气味和减少烟味。</p><h2>眨眼迷你 2 件装</h2><p><core-commerce id="de7159c6f0a24ac880e5a06fca85d87d" data-type="product-list"></core-commerce></p><p>两件装<a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:57;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI2NmVhNTY3YS1jOTg3LTRjMmUtYTJmZi0wMjkwNGVmZGU2ZWEiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYW1hem9uLmNvbS9kcC9CMDdYMjdWSzNEP3RhZz1nZGd0MGMtcC1vLTEzNi0yMCIsImNvbnRlbnRVdWlkIjoiYWFkZDA1OTYtMTYwYi00ZWUyLWIyMDQtODEzNmFhYjljZTYzIn0&amp;signature=AQAAAWF9dQZugGLX-IQ73hXlMgBDYb1JPCEhieLPv8xu6-9Y&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fdp%2FB07X27VK3D" class="rapid-with-clickid">Blink Mini 安全摄像头</a>在 Prime Day 促销，售价为 34 美元。这仅比去年假日购物季的价格高出 4 美元。虽然这些摄像头是有线的，但它们具有与标准无线 Blink 摄像头相同的大部分功能，包括 1080p 视频录制以及对双向通话和动作警报的支持。</p><p><strong><em>您的 Prime 会员日购物指南</em></strong><em>：查看我们所有的</em><a data-i13n="cpos:58;pos:1" href="https://www.yahoo.com/topics/prime-day/"><em>Prime 会员日</em></a><em>报道。</em><em>在雅虎生活上</em><em>购买</em><a data-i13n="cpos:59;pos:1" href="https://www.yahoo.com/lifestyle/prime-day-2023-191047652.html"><em>最优惠的 Prime Day 优惠</em></a>。<em>关注 Engadget，了解</em><a data-i13n="cpos:60;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/amazon-prime-day-2023-124519231.html"><em>亚马逊 Prime Day 最佳科技优惠</em></a><em>。</em>在 In the Know 上<em>了解</em><a data-i13n="cpos:61;pos:1" href="https://www.intheknow.com/tag/prime-day/"><em>Prime Day 趋势</em></a><em>。聆听 Autoblog 的汽车专家讲述与汽车相关的</em><a data-i13n="cpos:62;pos:1" href="https://www.autoblog.com/article/amazon-prime-day-2023/"><em>Prime Day 必买优惠</em></a><em>，并</em><em>在 AOL 上查找</em><a data-i13n="cpos:63;pos:1" href="https://www.aol.com/lifestyle/amazon-prime-day-090057255.html"><em>Prime Day 促销信息</em></a>，这些都是专为您精心挑选的。</p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上：https://www.engadget.com/the-best-amazon-prime-day-deals