。 Series 8 是我们<a data-i13n="cpos:28;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/best-smartwatches-153013118.html">最喜欢的智能手表</a>，因为它具有详细的健康和健身跟踪功能，以及与 iPhone 应用程序和通知的无缝集成。温度传感器、心电图和血氧读数以及改进的睡眠指标等新功能为您提供比以往更多的数据，而碰撞检测可以在您发生事故时寻求帮助。 <a data-i13n="cpos:29;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/the-apple-watch-embraces-widgets-again-in-watchos-10-180838970.html">即将推出的 WatchOS 10</a>将添加小部件和扩展功能，包括在正念应用程序中跟踪您的心情的方法。</p><h2>苹果手表 SE </h2><p><core-commerce id="27dc535f038c40e5bd006062163a2ae4" data-type="product-list"></core-commerce></p><p> <a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:30;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI2NmVhNTY3YS1jOTg3LTRjMmUtYTJmZi0wMjkwNGVmZGU2ZWEiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYW1hem9uLmNvbS9kcC9CMEJESFRRRFJaLz90YWc9Z2RndDBjLXAtby0xOTgtMjAiLCJjb250ZW50VXVpZCI6IjU2ZDlmODlkLTVhZjktNDI3YS1iMTVmLTFlOTk3YzVhYjAwZiJ9&amp;signature=AQAAAcN2CNpGpWlhxKeYOiUCmgomh7frnTHnSqIOO7scZuPM&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fdp%2FB0BDHTQDRZ%2F" class="rapid-with-clickid">Apple Watch SE</a>是 Apple 的廉价智能手表，通常售价为 250 美元。 Prime Day 折扣使得 40 毫米尺寸的售价仅为 200 美元。 <a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:31;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI2NmVhNTY3YS1jOTg3LTRjMmUtYTJmZi0wMjkwNGVmZGU2ZWEiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYW1hem9uLmNvbS9kcC9CMEJESFFUMTFWP3RhZz1nZGd0MGMtcC1vLTE5OC0yMCIsImNvbnRlbnRVdWlkIjoiNTZkOWY4OWQtNWFmOS00MjdhLWIxNWYtMWU5OTdjNWFiMDBmIn0&amp;signature=AQAAARl2Psgm_AsHjHzFj3jFzQ6zX41fqDf-__DmBlhwZPWB&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fdp%2FB0BDHQT11V" class="rapi