-review-mac-monitor-154504997.html">我们仍然认为</a>该显示屏仅适合真正的苹果爱好者。内部的 A13 仿生芯片使其比大多数显示器更智能，但 60Hz 刷新率令人失望。尽管如此，它的构造还是不错的，有好的扬声器和明亮准确的屏幕。</p><p><strong><em>您的 Prime 会员日购物指南</em></strong><em>：查看我们所有的</em><a data-i13n="cpos:43;pos:1" href="https://www.yahoo.com/topics/prime-day/"><em>Prime 会员日</em></a><em>报道。</em><em>在雅虎生活上</em><em>购买</em><a data-i13n="cpos:44;pos:1" href="https://www.yahoo.com/lifestyle/prime-day-2023-191047652.html"><em>最优惠的 Prime Day 优惠</em></a>。<em>关注 Engadget，了解</em><a data-i13n="cpos:45;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/amazon-prime-day-2023-124519231.html"><em>亚马逊 Prime Day 最佳科技优惠</em></a><em>。</em>在 In the Know 上<em>了解</em><a data-i13n="cpos:46;pos:1" href="https://www.intheknow.com/tag/prime-day/"><em>Prime Day 趋势</em></a><em>。聆听 Autoblog 的汽车专家讲述与汽车相关的</em><a data-i13n="cpos:47;pos:1" href="https://www.autoblog.com/article/amazon-prime-day-2023/"><em>Prime Day 必买优惠</em></a><em>，并</em><em>在 AOL 上查找</em><a data-i13n="cpos:48;pos:1" href="https://www.aol.com/lifestyle/amazon-prime-day-090057255.html"><em>Prime Day 促销信息</em></a>，这些都是专为您精心挑选的。</p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上：https://www.engadget.com/best-prime-day-apple-deals-on-airpods-macbooks-and-more-110302021.html?src=rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/best-prime-day-apple-deals-on-airpods-macbooks-and-more-110302021.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> 56d9f89d-5af9-427a-b15f-1e997c5ab00f</guid><dc:creator>艾米·斯科海姆</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>恩杰特</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder>恩杰特</dc:rightsholder><pubDate>Tue, 11 Jul 2023 11:03:02 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1689073386</ingested><modified> 2023-07-11T11:03:27+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Information Technology]]></category><category><![CDATA[Technology & Electronics]]></category><category><![CDATA[Handheld & Connected Devices]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CD